ygData.messageBody:
To complete the gnoll fang quest, you hand
moonstones in to Fish Ranamer at Fish's Ale Tavern, located
by the docks in South Qeynos.<br><br>Also, the
captain of the guard is Captain Tillin, who looks just
like a regular guard and is in the Arena in South
Qeynos.<br><br>You won't make a ton of money off of gnoll fangs, but
the exp is good and the money is more or less a
bonus.<br><br>Wisps and lightstones are absolutely amazing at your
level, though.
